  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个AXI4 Lite主写通道的监控模块，核心需求是追踪写事务并检测超时。整体结构我想分成三个主要部分：AXIL通道层、监控核心、以及输出接口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "axil4_master_wr_mon",
        "Output"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，AXIL通道层具体包含哪些信号？是标准的AW、W、B三个通道吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是写地址AW、写数据W和写响应B。这三个通道都需要接入监控核心。监控核心内部我打算再细分两层：底层是事务追踪和超时检测，上层是报告生成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把顶层结构画出来。AXIL Master Channels作为一个子图，包含AW、W、B三个通道节点。然后axil4_master_wr_mon是另一个子图，内部嵌套Monitor Base和Reporter两个子图。Monitor Base里放TRANS和TIMEOUT，Reporter里放PKT。最后Output子图输出MONBUS。这样层级关系对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AXIL_Channels",
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B",
        "axil4_master_wr_mon",
        "Base",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "Reporter",
        "PKT",
        "Output",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "层级是对的，但有个细节：MONBUS的位宽要标注清楚，是64-bit的packet格式，命名用mon_*表示这是监控总线输出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已更新，MONBUS标注为mon_*(64-bit packets)。现在处理数据流：AW、W、B三个通道都汇入TRANS，然后TRANS到TIMEOUT，TIMEOUT触发PKT，最后PKT输出到MONBUS。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B",
        "TRANS",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT",
        "MONBUS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "数据流方向没问题，但我想确认一下：TRANS同时接收AW和W的输入，这意味着我们要追踪地址和数据的配对，对吧？B通道的响应也要回传到TRANS做完成确认？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，AW和W进入TRANS进行事务组装，B响应返回确认事务完成。如果超时未收到B响应，TIMEOUT就会触发，走PKT生成错误报告。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TRANS",
        "AW",
        "W",
        "B",
        "TIMEOUT",
        "PKT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
